ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectWheat ** August 2011 - July 2012 ** INITIAL PAYMENTS **
PrecisOrder (1) repealing order P.C. 2012-59 of February 2, 2012 and (2) approving sums fixed by the Canadian Wheat Board to establish the initial payments for grades other than the base grade of WHEAT for the pool period commencing on August 1, 2011 and ending on July 31, 2012.
